            <description><![CDATA[<style>
  body { font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; padding: 12px; }
  h3 { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 14px; }
  ul { margin: 4px 0; padding-left: 20px; }
  li { margin: 2px 0; }
</style>
<h3>What's New</h3>
<ul>
  <li> fixes a crash related to projects</li>
<li> rearranges the git pane by moving the commit button to the right of the commit field, moves push up top and adds pull next to it</li>
<li> plumbing for Turm package</li> 
<li> fixes code reviews popping up all the fucking time</li>
<li> fixes a couple of overlapping pin icons </li>
<li> adds auto and manual merge conflicts to git pane</li> 
<li> fixes pinned pane popover single click not registering</li> 
<li> adds special server overlay</li>
<li> adds build variant to server overlay</li> 
<li> fixes global mcp write and writes to projects </li>
</ul>
]]></description>
